
SOURCE
https://thenextweb.com/artificial-intelligence/2017/11/13/alibabas-ai-is-the-blueprint-for-brick-and-mortar-stores-of-the-future/
AGENT
Alibaba Developers
GOAL
To help customers with clothing and accessory suggestions on the items they are trying.Which no real staff can remember every shopping detail of all customers.
DATA
Massive amounts of shopping data
METHODS
ML to recognize hundreds of millions of items of clothing with the tastes of designers and fashion experts.
RESULTS
FashionAI returns dozens of outfit matches for the chosen items of the customer is trying in the same store.
COMMENTS
This is still in trying process but can change the shopping for good.
